  Hotel Description

Nestled in the heart of District 1 - Pham Ngu Lao / Tay Balo, Elios Hotel is an ideal spot from which to discover Ho Chi Minh City. From here, guests can enjoy easy access to all that the lively city has to offer. With its convenient location, the hotel offers easy access to the city's must-see destinations.

At Elios Hotel, every effort is made to make guests feel comfortable. To do so, the hotel provides the best in services and amenities. To name a few of the hotel's facilities, there are newspapers, elevator, tours, Wi-Fi in public areas, business center.

In addition, all guestrooms feature a variety of comforts such as separate shower and tub, internet access – wireless (complimentary), hair dryer, non smoking rooms, desk to please even the most discerning guest. The complete list of recreational facilities is available at the hotel, including fitness center. Discover an engaging blend of professional service and a wide array of features at Elios Hotel.
